{% block content %}
    {% include '../layouts/nav/_nav_side.twig' with {data: page_accessibility.nav_side} %}
    {% include '../components/sections/section_heading_top.twig' with {data: page_accessibility.heading} %}

    <div class="row section_heading_bottom bg-blue-3">
        <div class="col px-0">
            <div class="container cont-site d-flex flex-column justify-content-center h-100">
                <div>
                    <p class="text_heading_main text-white-1 mb-0">At Plenco, we’re committed to accessibility. It is our policy to ensure that everyone, including persons with disabilities, has full and <span class='text-blue-l2'>equal access to our digital offerings</span>.</p>
                </div> 
                <div>                     
                    <p class="text_heading_add pt-4 text-white-1"></p> 
                </div>                
            </div>
        </div>2
    </div>



    <div class="section_106">
        <div>
            <div class="subheader">Our website strives to meet the following accessibility standards: <a href="#">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.0 AA, PDF/Universal Accessibility (PDF/UA)</a> to ensure our digital offerings are ADA Compliant.</div>                
            <p>Here are just some of the many ways that our website is accessible and meets the above accessibility standards:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Background and foreground colors are made to have high contrast ratios</li>
                <li>Buttons have discernible names</li>
                <li>Clean, efficient coding practices</li>
                <li>Descriptive alt tags are set on all meaningful images</li>
                <li>We use a focus indicator to highlight interactable elements</li>
                <li>We maintain a consistent and maintainable layout throughout the website</li>                    
            </ul>
            <p>Plenco and it’s developers are committed to accessibility and we are always seeking to improve. If you know of a way we can improve, we’d love to hear more. You can email the developers of this site at <a href="mailto:info@fifthcolor.com" class="text-black-1" style="font-family: 'Mulish-600';">info@fifthcolor.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div> 


    
    
       







    

